      <title>GAMES101_Work01</title>
      <link>https://GeeTeng.github.io/post/graphic_work01/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://GeeTeng.github.io/post/graphic_work01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;2d-transformations&#34;&gt;2D Transformations&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;scale&#34;&gt;Scale&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;$$&#xD;&#xA;S(s_x, s_y) = &#xD;&#xA;\begin{pmatrix}&#xD;&#xA;s_x &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\&#xD;&#xA;0 &amp; s_y &amp; 0 \\&#xD;&#xA;0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &#xD;&#xA;\end{pmatrix}&#xD;&#xA;$$&lt;h4 id=&#34;rotation&#34;&gt;Rotation&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;$$&#xD;&#xA;R(\alpha) = \begin{pmatrix} \cos \alpha &amp; -\sin \alpha &amp; 0 \\ \sin \alpha &amp; \cos \alpha &amp; 0 \\ 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 \end{pmatrix}&#xD;&#xA;$$&lt;h4 id=&#34;translation&#34;&gt;Translation&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;$$&#xD;&#xA;T(t_x, t_y) = \begin{pmatrix} 1 &amp; 0 &amp; t_x \\ 0 &amp; 1 &amp; t_y \\ 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 \end{pmatrix}&#xD;&#xA;$$&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;齐次坐标的最后一位为 0 表示方向或无穷远点&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GAMES101_Work0</title>
      <link>https://GeeTeng.github.io/post/graphic_work0/</link>
